7. Add plain-text fallback
8. Test with various error types

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] All FastMCP error types are categorized
- [ ] Each category has distinct visual styling
- [ ] Suggestions are relevant and actionable
- [ ] Error codes are assigned consistently
- [ ] Backtrace display is conditional
- [ ] Plain-text fallback is functional
- [ ] No emoji in plain-text mode

## Dependencies

